==Scales==
As they level, non-"monstrous" [[demonspawn]] naturally receive three ranks of a single scales mutation; other sources of mutation will only give the scales they would get naturally. [[Draconian]]s have natural scales independent of these mutations, and are unable to gain other scales. Currently only checked for iridescent scales, this may be a bug.

